hits.definition:
坐

[zuò] seat, sit, travel by (car/plane/etc.), put a kettle (or similar) on the fire, <classifier for bridges, buildings, etc.>;

    请坐 qǐngzuò please have a seat;

    坐公共汽车 zuò gōngòng qìchē ride a bus

集

[jí] (= 收集 shōují) collect;

    集中 jízhōng centralize

黑

[hēi] (= 黑色 hēisè) black;

黑暗 hēi'àn dark

随 (F 隨)

[suí] follow;

    随便 suíbiàn as you like
